what are the 'would be' ingredients in butter beer and dont just write 'butter and beer' what do you imagine it to taste like ingredients pint real vanilla ice cream use a brand that includes vanilla seed specks for best flavor or make your own cup real butter at room temperature teaspoon butterscotch extract cup brown sugar teaspoon ground cinnamon teaspoon freshly grated nutmeg quart apple cider preparation on medium speed beat together vanilla ice cream butter butterscotch extract brown sugar cinnamon and nutmeg until well combined pour into a container and re freeze when ready to serve gently heat apple cider in a saucepan until steaming hot place scoop of ice cream in a thick soda glass or large mug top with steaming apple cider yield to servings Coffee Tea Cider Bread Ice cream Rice pudding Beer Halva Apple pie Chocolate Nutmeg Japanese cuisine Vinegar Breakfast Curry Wine Milkshake Brewery Cuisine of Denmark Cuisine of the Philippines Vanilla Barbecue Cold Stone Creamery Cocoa Cooking weights and measures Maple syrup Root beer Haggis Espresso Turkish coffee Soft drink Jelly Belly Milk Cinnamon Ketchup Pancake Recipe Root beer float Potato Idli Cuisine of Brazil Sundae Cuisine of Singapore Jewish cuisine Dairy Cookware and bakeware French cuisine Custard Perfume Hot dog Apple Polish cuisine Bagel Soul food French toast Mayonnaise Ramen Chili con carne Cuisine of Africa In-N-Out Burger Alcoholic beverage Horehound Volume Sauce Martini cocktail Fanta Champagne (beverage) Toffee Guinness Cajun cuisine Sushi Carbon dioxide Cooking Kit Kat Cream (food) Popcorn Mead Bengali cuisine Cuisine of Malaysia Diet soda Cha chaan teng Twix Baked Alaska Glass Sangr__a Peanut butter McDonald's Cuisine of the Southern United States Cantonese cuisine Snapple 